{"tid":844993,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"加利·連尼加：美斯明顯就不是一個人類","createTime":"2018-10-02T10:16:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T13:57:45.000Z","uid":20634,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e4e6dedba297cdff0625576c515a3eb00589629a","tid":844993,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:16:46.000Z","msg":"　　連尼加是美斯的超級球迷，最近他又對美斯做出了評價，在他看來，美斯就是有史以來最出色的球員。<br />\n<br />\n　　連尼加表示：「美斯顯然不是人類。所有人都知道我是一個美斯粉絲，我認為他就是有史以來最好的球員。」<br />\n<br />\n　　「當我看他踢球，我仍然會因他的一系列操作而如癡如醉，好像他在踢球時能俯瞰球場。他是我見過的最好的突破手，最有想像力的球員，技術最好的球員，也是傳球最好的球員之一。當你擁有了所有這些能力，那顯然就不是人類了。」<br />\n<br />\n　　同時他也對美斯的球品讚賞有加：「他<span style=\"color: red;\">從不演戲，從不插水，從不報復</span>，完全是一個足球的化身。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQNdfGe5bzU8WPJfRVPnka_KDNNeh1C-oDlUxgVfzXolo-L79rD\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcQNdfGe5bzU8WPJfRVPnka_KDNNeh1C-oDlUxgVfzXolo-L79rD&h=9c832532&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0288ecfde9a4119ec6c2e1128345aab3f93c341c","tid":844993,"uid":5649,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:20:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.dailymail.co.uk/i/pix/2015/08/05/23/2B21652700000578-3186462-The_28_year_old_then_grabbed_the_towering_France_international_b-a-20_1438815252536.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.dailymail.co.uk%2Fi%2Fpix%2F2015%2F08%2F05%2F23%2F2B21652700000578-3186462-The_28_year_old_then_grabbed_the_towering_France_international_b-a-20_1438815252536.jpg&h=816666cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n芝娃娃從不報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"355a421c176394ee7ae760075be8b611bd9df4b5","tid":844993,"uid":5649,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:20:49.000Z","msg":"不像某人，無緣前三照去！美斯將參加FIFA頒獎典禮<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/830575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/830575